column8: Cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Snow possible above 1300 metres. Winds southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h. Daytime maximum temperatures between 9 and 19.

Cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Snow possible above 1500 metres. Winds southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light early in the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 11 and 19.

Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Snow possible above 1800 metres. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to between 5 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 14 and 21.

Mostly sunny morning. Patchy morning fog in the north. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to between 5 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 16 and 22.
